data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious and inviting 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Nestled within the stunning landscape of Shorewood, this property boasts a beautiful lot adorned with mature trees that create a tranquil oasis. Imagine a lifestyle where you can relish the beauty of your private haven while being connected to nature and recreational opportunities. This property offers the best of both worlds: a spacious and well-appointed home, along with the joys of an outdoor enthusiast's paradise just steps away. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this house your forever home.
